"Hey, there goes our lunch! Hmmm, they are stronger than we thought, let’s go "
"tell Master."
msgstr "嘿，那裡有我們的餐點！嗯，他們比我們想像得更強，讓我們去通知主人。"

#. [message]: role=Supporter
#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/03_To_the_Mines.cfg:184
